name: Rhyfel: Game of Corporate Domination
blurb: Ready-to-play sandbox strategy game. Players are corporate CEOs competing in a world without a government. Social. MMO. Multi-platform.

MERCHANT ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ In-game rewards: 10,000 Kickstarter food, two random legendary/purple harvesting installations, one Kickstarter Corporate Award, Rhyfel developers will be automatically added to your friends list.\r\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

HARVESTER ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~  
In-game rewards: one deed granting tile ownership, one Kickstarter Surplus Outlet installation, one Kickstarter Funding Office installation, two random legendary/purple installations.
